Theme Description

The Dexter Theme consists of 20+ Hi-Res Wallpapers, Custom Icons and select sounds from the Dexter Series. Dexter fans would immensely enjoy this one.

The Theme is based on Dexter TV Series- which has enjoyed wide critical acclaim and popularity. Season 4 aired its season finale on December 13, 2009 to a record-breaking audience of 2.6 million viewers, making it the most-watched original series episode ever on Showtime.

Michael C. Hall has won several awards for his portrayal of Dexter, including two Golden Globes and an Emmy.
